headline: CHIPOTLE CELEBRATES TEACHERS AND THE HEALTHCARE COMMUNITY WITH MORE THAN $2 MILLION IN FREE BURRITOS
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (NYSE: CMG) announced today it will recognize both teachers and healthcare workers by awarding 200,000 professionals with free burrito e-cards, equivalent to over $2 million in free food*. Since 2016, the company has given away more than $16 million in free Chipotle to educators and medical professionals.
